description: LibriVox recording of Hans Christian Andersen: Fairytales and Short Stories Volume 2, 1844 to 1847, by Hans Christian Andersen. A collection of some of Hans Christian Andersen's works. He is a Danish author and poet most famous for his fairy tales. (Summary by Kristingj) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
